        <Meaning id="a17b9643-b20c-42b9-9357-7cf0c3c95737" type="Noun">
          <Vi>Máy phát tia laze; tia laze</Vi>
          <En>A device that emits a narrow, intense beam of light through optical amplification; also refers to such a beam itself.</En>
          <Example>The surgeon used a laser to correct the patient’s vision.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="965915f5-c669-495e-a5d3-feb381849481">
